will triumph in china if we learn from their spirit of fearing 
no hardship and quietly contributing to the country and the 
people 
such exhortations have been common in the wake of last years 
prodemocracy movement which was violently crushed by the 
military hundreds perhaps thousands of people died 
this years spring festival celebrations in beijing seemed more 
subdued than in past years when the sound of firecrackers could be 
heard all night long 
traditionally chinese set off firecrackers for almost any 
special occasion but especially at the lunar new year because it 
