for tardiness and poor work 
ms fite said the employee showed an inability to write had 
a stubborn or immature attitude and prompted the personnel 
office to report she was driving them crazy complaining about 
things her work was just adequate ms fite said 
ms lewis contended that ms morrow became more demanding 
after she was made a permanent employee made increasing errors 
amid a further deterioration of attitude and conduct after a 
