capital plan to make sure their message will not be lost in the 
turmoil caused by mayor marion barrys cocaine possession arrest 
any tourists wishing to visit the vista hotel where barry 
allegedly smoked crack cocaine first will have to pass signs 
advising them that they are entering the nations last colony 
barrys arrest jan 18 on a federal charge of possessing cocaine 
has focused attention on his crumbling political fortunes and a 
possible mayoral candidacy by jesse jackson but it has also 
stirred a quieter debate over the impact on a longmoribund drive 
to make the city the 51st state 
