and vice premiers yao yilin and wu xueqian went to a food market in 
central beijing 
the national television news saturday evening showed each of 
them shaking hands making jokes and hugging babies in a 
campaignstumping style that has become common here only in the 
past few years 
the official term for such visits to homes and factories is 
going to the grass roots and it is an axiom of maoist 
communism that uniting with the masses is the only way to stay 
in power 
the leaders schedules were planned to include visits with 
