determination to continue its drastic austerity policy 
sharp reductions in credit and construction have slowed 
inflation but also have forced the closure of millions of rural 
factories urban factories remain open but in many the workers sit 
around playing cards and drinking tea because they lack electricity 
or raw materials 
li pledged the governments unremitting efforts to educate 
chinese in patriotism collectivism socialism selfreliance and 
hard struggle 
