people withstood a severe test and achieved a great victory in 
quelling the antigovernment rebellion in beijing last june he 
was referring to the massive prodemocracy demonstrations that were 
crushed by the army leaving hundreds and possible thousands dead 
we believe that the progressive cause of socialism has a 
